column5: The thing is she is sending mixed signals i rather have her just reject me right away it'll be better for me but no one minutes she wants to see me and hangout and the other she doesnt want to catch feelings but your right but ive been doing the alone thing for 20 years im getting tired of it i wanna pour my affection onto someone

Dark souls sounds right but im not the right piece for anyone im just tired of it i just want to cut off all emotions but can't well drinking makes me feel numb and makes me feel better and thanks internet stranger

That is how i feel no matter how many people i talk to the girl i want doesnt want to catch feelings cuz she been hurt and thanks for the support i appreciate it now i can drink knowing i aint the only one
That's one way i guess lol
Happened to me a few days ago on a night out on friends but they stopped me and pinned me down to prevent me from killing myself
